name: Slipstream Eel
text: If this card is Normal Summoned or Special Summoned: You can add 1 "Oh F!sh!" from your Deck to your hand. You can banish 1 Fish, Sea Serpent, or Aqua-type monster from your hand or field and target 1 card your opponent controls; return it to the hand. "You can only use each effect of "Slipstream Eel" once per turn.
